data.description: Excellent Opportunity For First Time Home Owners &/Or Investors looking for passive income! Great Home That Offers 3 Bed/2 Bath, A Pool, Granite Counters, Spacious Backyard & Much More! Arriving at this home you'll find a room near 5th an acre lot, an attached 2 car garage, and extra cement giving additional parking. Entering the home you are greeted with a bonus space that could be easily transformed into a 4th bedroom. The living room has a stone fireplace matching the stone from the exterior, LVT flooring, and built-in shelving adding character to the space. The laundry room is located off of the living room in-between the living room & garage. The kitchen has upgraded counters, a sink positioned to overlook the front yard, a breakfast bar, tons of cabinet space, an LVT floor extending from the living room to the kitchen, and overlooks the dining room. Down the hallway holds a full guest bathroom that has a shower with tile walls & 2 guest bedrooms that each have carpet. The primary bedroom has carpet flooring, a ceiling fan, a walk-in closet, and a private bathroom that has matching granite counters and, a tile step-in shower. This backyard has the potential to be an entertainer's dream, with extra cement from the back door extending to the pool while still providing yard space for, dog runs on the north side of the home. This home is located with easy access to Freeway 99, within a mile of Frank Kohn Elementary School, & parks. This is a must-see!
